\n仲有d厹又係好好笑，集體炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/170706_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F170706_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7cc4a650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/170716_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F170716_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ddfd22be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/170725_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F170725_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=068f1e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/170735_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F170735_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a7b69a81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有呀penny姐你點解要話人係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">水魚</span></span>呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/170927_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F170927_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=11c4b42c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，記住唔好做違法野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/171143_ea3dc39ca0